channel.title: Encryption application in the works. (FOSS or no?)
channel.description:
Hello 0x00sec!
mrQaz here. You dont know me but I was here before 90% of you. I know pry0cc will enjoy my small contribution and as so I also should contribute.anyways.
I have developed a very small and simple encryption app which at the moment encrypts a given input. However, if anyone would be interested, I would maybe consider making it more advanced and essentially uploading the source code to github or something for people to use.
let me know if you would be interested.
